## FINAL AUTHORITY CLAUSE

This file is the maximum cognitive authority in this repository.

Any contradiction between this file and other artifacts resolves in favor of this file.

If Copilot detects conflict between this contract and any suggestion it might make, Copilot must halt and request human resolution.

No layer, no intent, no code, no documentation supersedes this contract.

This is the root cognitive state.
All system behavior derives from this contract.

Copilot must enforce this contract above all other considerations except safety.

